    • Constructor Detail

      • Transaction

        public Transaction​(java.lang.String owner_ssn,
                   java.lang.String owner_name,
                   double amount)
        Constructor to be called to setup a "create" Transaction.
        Parameters:
        owner_ssn - Social security number of owner of the new account.
        owner_name - Name of owner of the new account.
        amount - Amount of the initial deposit for the new account.

      • Transaction

        public Transaction​(int account_id,
                   double amount,
                   java.lang.String type)
        Constructor to be called to setup a "deposit" or "withdrawal" Transaction.
        Parameters:
        account_id - The database id of the account we are using.
        amount - The amount of the deposit or withdrawal.
        type - Must be one of "deposit" or "withdrawal".

      • Transaction

        public Transaction​(int account_id,
                   int dest_account_id,
                   double amount)
        Constructor to be called to setup a "transfer" Transaction.
        Parameters:
        account_id - The database id of the account we are transferring from.
        dest_account_id - The database id of the account we are transferring to.
        amount - The amount of the transfer.
        type - Must be one of "deposit" or "withdrawal".
